</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-epAKVu bzHUyF pf-140_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-iLsJvT bAOpBE pf-141_">Implement comprehensive antenatal and postnatal care pathways
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-iLsJvT bAOpBE pf-143_">Ensure all staff are trained in emergency obstetric care and newborn resuscitation
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-iLsJvT bAOpBE pf-145_">Invest in infection prevention, hygiene, and facility safety
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-iLsJvT bAOpBE pf-147_">Provide trauma-informed care and support for postnatal mental health
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-iLsJvT bAOpBE pf-149_">Educate communities on reproductive health and safe childbirth options.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-feUYzb iXyfoG pf-151_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bJBfJu drQDYO pf-152_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-dExXmK Xerjk pf-153_">Recommendations
